1046
00:43:51,528 --> 00:43:55,432
I've never had a meal
for more than 15 to 20 minutes.

1047
00:43:55,499 --> 00:43:57,635
I got into a habit
of ordering something quick,

1048
00:43:57,701 --> 00:44:00,137
