1112
00:46:45,435 --> 00:46:46,436
It looks like soup.

1113
00:46:48,138 --> 00:46:50,307
He doesn't like dishes
that are too strong.

1114
00:46:50,374 --> 00:46:52,643
He doesn't like dishes
that are too strong.

1115
00:46:52,709 --> 00:46:54,144
-You can be honest.
-First of all,

1116
