1157
00:48:42,286 --> 00:48:44,421
<i>The crunchiness of the fish skin</i>
<i>adds texture,</i>

1158
00:48:44,488 --> 00:48:48,292
<i>the sourness, and the savory flavor</i>
<i>of the meat all become layered.</i>

1159
00:48:49,226 --> 00:48:54,197
I don't think you can cook anything
more perfect than this in just 13 minutes.

1160
00:48:54,264 --> 00:48:55,465
I see.

1161
00:48:55,532 --> 00:48:56,767
It was delicious.

1162
00:48:56,833 --> 00:48:58,936
Next up. Poong's Masterpiece.

1163
00:48:59,002 --> 00:49:03,407
Starch and soft tofu
