-Ongsimi?

1173
00:49:23,961 --> 00:49:24,995
It tastes just like that.

1174
00:49:25,062 --> 00:49:28,065
-I think the kick was the shrimp.
-The shrimp.

1175
00:49:28,131 --> 00:49:29,299
The shrimp.

1176
00:49:29,366 --> 00:49:33,003
-Also, it didn't taste fishy to me.
-I see.

1177
00:49:33,070 --> 00:49:33,904
See?

1178
00:49:33,971 --> 00:49:35,272
I was surprised with the cake.

1179
00:49:36,106 --> 00:49:37,274
He used starch,

1180
00:49:37,341 --> 00:49:40,744
